00:07:13.750 --> 00:07:14.340
Dongshan!

00:07:14.360 --> 00:07:15.140
I don't care.

00:07:15.310 --> 00:07:16.490
We can't hire court defaulters.

00:08:01.680 --> 00:08:02.610
This Yao Dongshan.

00:08:03.160 --> 00:08:04.050
I'm going to divorce him.

00:08:04.870 --> 00:08:05.490
Sister,

00:08:05.920 --> 00:08:07.370
Yao Dongshan has made me suffer my whole life

00:08:07.950 --> 00:08:08.660
and I'm okay with that

00:08:09.000 --> 00:08:09.490
but the children

00:08:09.920 --> 00:08:11.220
cannot suffer because of him.

00:08:11.600 --> 00:08:12.980
When Qian and Wei

00:08:13.000 --> 00:08:13.900
first started dating,

00:08:13.920 --> 00:08:15.690
I had been covering for him.

00:08:15.690 --> 00:08:17.640
I was afraid that Wei would despise her

00:08:17.640 --> 00:08:19.360
- and mess up the marriage after finding out. - Where are you?

00:08:19.430 --> 00:08:20.700
Your wife is here.

00:08:23.160 --> 00:08:23.980
Why is she there?

00:08:24.800 --> 00:08:25.290
Seriously.

00:08:25.720 --> 00:08:28.020
[Uncle Dongshan]
He had to become a government driver

00:08:28.070 --> 00:08:29.610
and they found out about his bad credit record.

00:08:30.000 --> 00:08:30.700
Doesn't he know

00:08:30.720 --> 00:08:32.220
that Wei is working with the government?

00:08:32.600 --> 00:08:33.490
Do Qian and I

00:08:33.510 --> 00:08:34.730
owe him in our previous lives?

00:08:35.320 --> 00:08:36.850
I don't care where you are hiding him

00:08:36.870 --> 00:08:37.580
today.

00:08:37.840 --> 00:08:38.820
I must find him.

00:08:39.030 --> 00:08:40.240
The problem is

00:08:40.240 --> 00:08:40.980
that I don't even know

00:08:41.000 --> 00:08:42.130
where he is.

00:08:42.670 --> 00:08:44.580
I even stopped square dancing.

00:08:44.790 --> 00:08:46.010
I am too embarrassed.

00:08:46.550 --> 00:08:47.980
I wanted to scold him

00:08:48.150 --> 00:08:48.980
but I missed the chance.

00:08:50.440 --> 00:08:50.940
Mom.

00:08:51.240 --> 00:08:51.730
Mom.

00:08:52.440 --> 00:08:53.250
If you want to scold, just do it.

00:08:54.240 --> 00:08:54.820
Vent your anger.

00:08:57.830 --> 00:08:58.340
Jiang Jialu,

00:08:58.340 --> 00:08:59.400
