00:09:33.630 --> 00:09:34.060
Hello.

00:09:34.480 --> 00:09:35.100
Jiaqi.

00:09:35.670 --> 00:09:36.300
Are you done with work?

00:09:36.960 --> 00:09:37.530
What's wrong?

00:09:37.910 --> 00:09:38.580
Let's have a chat.

00:09:59.620 --> 00:10:00.980
[Chen Ren]

00:10:02.540 --> 00:10:03.770
Shouldn't you pay up today?

00:10:04.620 --> 00:10:05.280
Where's the money?

00:10:05.720 --> 00:10:06.980
I transferred some of the money to you.

00:10:07.390 --> 00:10:08.700
I'll pay you the remaining amount in a few days.

00:10:09.960 --> 00:10:11.420
I already let you pay in installments.

00:10:11.600 --> 00:10:13.220
You're still trying to do installments within an installment?

00:10:14.720 --> 00:10:16.060
You must pay me no matter what...

00:10:26.020 --> 00:10:27.380
[Chen Ren]

00:10:34.910 --> 00:10:35.980
I prepared the money for you.

00:10:36.750 --> 00:10:38.610
I'll give it to you on the day Pang Jian leaves.

00:10:40.550 --> 00:10:41.610
But before he leaves,

00:10:42.390 --> 00:10:43.770
you must keep a close eye on Jiang Jiaqi.

00:10:44.220 --> 00:10:46.340
I don't want any surprises.

00:10:59.480 --> 00:11:00.730
Forget about that.

00:11:00.790 --> 00:11:02.390
Let's talk about your wife.

00:11:02.960 --> 00:11:04.410
She has been looking all over for you to get a divorce.

00:11:04.410 --> 00:11:04.940
What will you do?

00:11:05.440 --> 00:11:06.300
She might look agitated

00:11:07.030 --> 00:11:07.730
but she has been talking

00:11:07.750 --> 00:11:08.610
about a divorce for many years.

00:11:10.670 --> 00:11:11.890
Besides, I'm looking for a job

00:11:13.630 --> 00:11:14.850
for her sake.

00:11:15.200 --> 00:11:15.700
Because of her,

00:11:15.720 --> 00:11:17.460
I went to an interview to be a driver.

00:11:19.360 --> 00:11:21.300
I didn't know they would check my credit record

00:11:21.750 --> 00:11:23.370
before they hire me.

00:11:25.150 --> 00:11:25.650
Uncle,

00:11:27.000 --> 00:11:28.010
you've always

00:11:28.030 --> 00:11:29.130
meant well.

00:11:29.510 --> 00:11:30.730
But you just can't get anything done.

00:11:30.790 --> 00:11:31.940
Forget it.

00:11:32.360 --> 00:11:33.530
We're almost the same.

00:11:33.870 --> 00:11:34.820
No one should laugh at others.

00:11:36.360 --> 00:11:37.890
Why did I call Jiaqi?

00:11:37.960 --> 00:11:39.530
I want to feel

00:11:39.750 --> 00:11:40.580
and breathe

00:11:40.870 --> 00:11:42.490
the air of a successful person.

00:11:44.200 --> 00:11:45.220
What's so good about me?

00:11:46.510 --> 00:11:47.700
What's good about you?

00:11:49.630 --> 00:11:51.490
You are a manager of a company.

00:11:52.000 --> 00:11:53.300
Your wife is good-looking

00:11:53.670 --> 00:11:54.300
and capable.

00:11:55.080 --> 00:11:56.010
Most importantly,

00:11:56.320 --> 00:11:57.060
there's also a girl

00:11:57.120 --> 00:11:58.340
who likes you in your office.

00:12:00.320 --> 00:12:01.250
Why do you mention this again?

00:12:01.320 --> 00:12:02.060
Just stop it.

00:12:02.550 --> 00:12:04.850
You knew her before you lost the money.

00:12:06.240 --> 00:12:07.220
Did you two know each other for a long time?

00:12:13.120 --> 00:12:14.460
I arranged for her to join Sen'an.

00:12:19.630 --> 00:12:20.420
The HR department

00:12:20.440 --> 00:12:21.770
sent many resumes to me back then.

00:12:23.120 --> 00:12:24.250
They were

00:12:24.320 --> 00:12:26.650
all embellished with multiple work experiences.

00:12:28.750 --> 00:12:29.730
